m_q.target_metric: average number of laps driven in the Indianapolis 500 in Tony Gulotta's career
sub_questions: How many Indianapolis 500 races did Tony Gulotta participate in?
What is the total number of laps driven across all races?
What is the sum of laps divided by number of races?

format_notes: All columns are stored as object/string dtype
Laps column needs conversion to numeric
Sample data shows 23 total rows representing race entries

constraints: Laps column must be numeric and non-negative
Only count races where Laps value is valid/non-null
Each row represents one Indianapolis 500 race entry
derived_filters: Exclude rows where Laps cannot be converted to numeric
Include all rows as they represent Indianapolis 500 races
output_format_requirements: Result should be a single numeric value
Should represent average laps per race
Round to reasonable precision (e.g., 2 decimal places)
